 <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> result<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>😊</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EB%A7%81%ED%81%AC\">문제 링크</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4\">조건</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%9E%85%EB%A0%A5%EA%B0%92\">입력값</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5%EA%B0%92\">출력값</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95\">풀이과정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C\">코드</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 28, 2022","title":"양궁대회","categories":"PS","author":"chanjook1m","emoji":"😊"},"fields":{"slug":"/2022-kakao-blind-4/"}},"prev":{"id":"2a9fad7e-6acd-569a-a7df-c7f883232062","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"drop-of-water\"\n        title=\"drop-of-water\"\n        src=\"/static/b1e5e81fab78475ab36e97668d96b66a/80e3c/drop-of-water.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b1e5e81fab78475ab36e97668d96b66a/4ec73/drop-of-water.jpg 180w,\n/static/b1e5e81fab78475ab36e97668d96b66a/158ba/drop-of-water.jpg 360w,\n/static/b1e5e81fab78475ab36e97668d96b66a/80e3c/drop-of-water.jpg 720w,\n/static/b1e5e81fab78475ab36e97668d96b66a/47311/drop-of-water.jpg 1080w,\n/static/b1e5e81fab78475ab36e9